Timothy Patrick Murphy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timothy_Patrick_Murphy 0 Timothy Patrick Murphy (November 3, 1959 – December 6, 1988) was an American actor, perhaps best known for his role as Mickey Trotter on the popular CBS prime time soap opera Dallas from 1982–83.
